B.Uc=new A.G(B.Z,["King Fahd Fountain","The tallest fountain in the world at 312 meters, overlooking the Red Sea with animated lights at night. One of Jeddah's main landmarks.","Jeddah Corniche, Al Hamra District","Open 24 hours for external viewing","\u2022 Best time to visit is after Maghrib when the lights turn on\n\u2022 Take a boat tour to enjoy the view"],t.w)
B.Uf=new A.G(B.Z,["Al-Balad (Historic Jeddah)","UNESCO World Heritage Site. Old ornate houses, narrow alleys, and a traditional souq reflecting old Jeddah's spirit.","Historic Jeddah center, near the port","Shops 10 AM - 10 PM","\u2022 Wear comfortable clothes for walking\n\u2022 Avoid going during hot midday"],t.w)
B.Uq=new A.G(B.Z,["Jeddah Corniche","Modern corniche along the Red Sea with walking paths, playgrounds, and parks. Ideal for families and sports.","Jeddah Corniche, north of the beach","Open 24 hours","\u2022 Rent a bicycle for the ride\n\u2022 Watch the sunset from the walkway"],t.w)
B.U5=new A.G(B.Z,["Abdul Raouf Khalil Museum","Large heritage museum showcasing Jeddah and Hijaz history through Islamic art and rare artifacts.","Al Rawdah District, Jeddah","Sat - Thu 9 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Allocate at least 2 hours for the visit\n\u2022 Photography allowed in some wings"],t.w)
B.Up=new A.G(B.Z,["Nasseef House","Heritage palace from the 19th century that hosted King Abdulaziz. Distinctive wooden balconies and authentic Hejazi design.","Al-Balad, Al Yamama District","Sun - Thu 9 AM - 5 PM","\u2022 Free guided tour available\n\u2022 Take photos of the wooden balconies"],t.w)
B.Ug=new A.G(B.Z,["Al Baik Restaurants","Famous Saudi chain for fast food, known for fried chicken and local dishes.","Multiple branches in Jeddah","Most branches 7 AM - 2 AM","\u2022 Try the Al Baik Special meal\n\u2022 Family and kid friendly"],t.w)
B.Um=new A.G(B.Z,["Food Line Restaurant","International restaurant on the corniche with sea views and varied cuisine.","Jeddah Corniche","12 PM - 12 AM","\u2022 Book ahead on holidays\n\u2022 Request a table with sea view"],t.w)
B.Uh=new A.G(B.Z,["Mama Noura Restaurant","Heritage restaurant for authentic Hejazi cuisine. Kabsa, Mandi, and unique stews in a traditional setting.","Al-Balad","12 PM - 11 PM","\u2022 Try the Hejazi Kabsa\n\u2022 Family-friendly and relaxed atmosphere"],t.w)
B.U2=new A.G(B.Z,["Tiger's Den Restaurant","Famous burger restaurant with creative recipes and high quality.","King Abdulaziz Road","11 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Try the signature burger\n\u2022 Family meals available"],t.w)
B.U6=new A.G(B.Z,["Herfy Restaurant","Local chain for fast food and drinks. Affordable prices and quick service.","Multiple branches","24 hours at most branches","\u2022 Budget-friendly option\n\u2022 Good for a quick stop"],t.w)
B.Uk=new A.G(B.Z,["Park Hyatt Jeddah","Luxury five-star hotel on the corniche. Sea views and premium service.","Jeddah Corniche","24-hour reception","\u2022 Request a room with sea view\n\u2022 Spa and pool are excellent"],t.w)
B.U9=new A.G(B.Z,["M\xf6venpick Jeddah","Luxury hotel in central Jeddah, close to malls and landmarks.","King Fahd Road","24-hour reception","\u2022 Central location for getting around\n\u2022 Varied and distinctive breakfast"],t.w)
B.Ud=new A.G(B.Z,["Rosewood Jeddah","Elegant hotel with classic design overlooking the Red Sea.","Al Hamra District","24-hour reception","\u2022 Luxury hotel experience\n\u2022 Fine dining restaurant worth a visit"],t.w)
B.U8=new A.G(B.Z,["Crowne Plaza Jeddah","Family and business-friendly hotel. Spacious rooms and full facilities.","Al Zahra District","24-hour reception","\u2022 Reasonable rates\n\u2022 Close to shopping malls"],t.w)
B.Un=new A.G(B.Z,["Fakieh Aquarium","Largest aquarium in Saudi Arabia. Thousands of fish and marine life in glass tunnels underwater.","Madinah Road, Al Faisaliyah District","10 AM - 10 PM","\u2022 Especially suitable for children\n\u2022 Allow 2-3 hours for the visit"],t.w)
B.U3=new A.G(B.Z,["Prince Metroob Park","Large public park in the heart of Jeddah with walking paths, sports facilities, and family picnic areas. One of the most visited parks.","Al Rawdah District, Jeddah","6 AM - 11 PM","\u2022 Ideal for walking and sports in the morning\n\u2022 Has children's playgrounds"],t.w)
B.U4=new A.G(B.Z,["Al Jawhara Zoo Park","Zoo and amusement park for families. Local and international animals plus an amusement city.","Al Jawhara District","4 PM - 11 PM (varies in summer)","\u2022 Check opening times\n\u2022 Suitable for families with children"],t.w)
B.Ub=new A.G(B.Z,["Red Sea Mall","One of the largest malls in Jeddah. International brands, cinema, and amusement park.","Makkah-Jeddah Highway","10 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Spacious parking\n\u2022 IMAX cinema available"],t.w)
B.Ua=new A.G(B.Z,["Arab Mall","Massive mall for international brands. Modern design and entertainment facilities.","Madinah Road","10 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Plan a day for shopping\n\u2022 Varied food court"],t.w)
B.Uj=new A.G(B.Z,["City Walk","Open-air market on the corniche. Shops and restaurants with sea views.","Jeddah Corniche","10 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Walk the corniche after shopping\n\u2022 Beautiful evening atmosphere"],t.w)
B.Ui=new A.G(B.Z,["Al-Balad Souq","Heritage souq for antiques, spices, and perfumes. Historic shopping experience.","Al-Balad","9 AM - 10 PM","\u2022 Negotiate on prices\n\u2022 Buy spices and perfumes as souvenirs"],t.w)
B.U7=new A.G(B.Z,["Jeddah Sculpture Museum","Open-air art museum for contemporary sculptures on Jeddah Corniche.","Jeddah Corniche","Open 24 hours","\u2022 Free visit\n\u2022 Great photo opportunities of the sculptures"],t.w)
B.Ur=new A.G(B.Z,["Jeddah Season","Seasonal events with concerts, shows, and exhibitions. Check the program before visiting.","Various locations in Jeddah","According to program","\u2022 Follow the events program\n\u2022 Book ahead for concerts"],t.w)
B.Uo=new A.G(B.Z,["Jeddah Theater","Theater shows and cultural festivals. Destination for arts and performance.","Jeddah Corniche","According to program","\u2022 Book tickets in advance\n\u2022 Varied program for families"],t.w)
B.Ul=new A.G(B.Z,["Center Point","Entertainment center and amusement park for kids and adults. Electronic and fun games.","King Abdulaziz Road","10 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Credit cards for play\n\u2022 Games for all ages"],t.w)
B.Ue=new A.G(B.Z,["Riyadh City Boulevard","Integrated entertainment area: restaurants, shopping, cinema, and amusement park in one place.","Al Rawdah District","10 AM - 12 AM","\u2022 Plan a half-day visit\n\u2022 Variety for the whole family"],t.w)
